  <div class="content">

    
    
            
                    <a href="/content/one-hand-slapping" class="imagecache imagecache-teaser imagecache-linked imagecache-teaser_linked"></a>        
        

<p>
Adobe Systems, the world's leading supplier of graphical software, is gradually
shifting its business to a subscription model, baiting customers with features
and tools available only to <a href="http://html.adobe.com/edge/creativecloud">Creative Cloud subscribers</a>.<span class="read-more"><a href="/content/one-hand-slapping"> more>></a></span></p>
