<p class="MsoNormal">Spring Break is upon us, and the destination of choice for geeks to take their annual spring sojourn is the South by Southwest Interactive Festival in Austin.&nbsp; Not all those who wish to go will get the expense approved and instead will end up stuck sifting through a barrage of blog posts and event hashtags in order to get their SXSW fix.<span class="read-more"><a href="/content/contest-takes-sxsw-experience-outside-austin"> more>></a></span></p>

